%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import year, mean, month
df=df_pt_address\
    .join(df_cw, df_pt_address.changwat==df_cw.changwat )\
    .select('hn', 'name')\
    .withColumnRenamed('name','cw_name')

df=df.join(df_pt,"hn")\
    .select('hn','cw_name','male','occptn')\
    .join(df_oc,'occptn')\
    .withColumnRenamed('name','oc_name')\
    .select('hn','cw_name','male','oc_name')
    
df=df.join(df_pv, df.cw_name==df_pv.CHANGWAT_T)\
    .drop(df_pv.CHANGWAT_T)
    
basedf=df.join(df_ar,"hn")
df=basedf\
    .groupby('cw_name','oc_name','male',year('ardate').alias("year"), month('ardate').alias("month"))\
    .agg({'invamt':'sum'})\
    .orderBy('sum(invamt)')
z.show(df)
df.registerTempTable("debt")
